                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18171203-52-off265 t18171203-52-cd266"></join>, one watch, value 3l.; one chain, value 30s.; two seals, value 10s., and one key, value 4d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18171203-52-victim372" type="victimName">
